      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be documented with version control, regression testing, and traceable release notes consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent v2022R2 is used under a validated institutional license. Version control and regression test suite documentation are on file. Software QA procedures satisfy MRL 2 requirements."
    },
    {
