      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which is geometrically representative of the COU device. Operating conditions (flow rates 2–7 L/min, speeds 2000–3500 RPM) span the COU envelope. Blood analog fluid properties match within accepted tolerances."
    },
    {
