      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence must be demonstrated with residuals reduced by at least 4 orders of magnitude and monitored QoI values stabilized.",
      "rationale": "All simulations were run to residual convergence of 1e-5 for continuity and momentum equations. Hemolysis index monitor values were tracked over iterations and confirmed stable within 0.1% over the final 500 iterations."
    },
