      "rationale": "Simulation setup documentation was reviewed by a senior CFD analyst not involved in the original model construction. Boundary condition assignments, turbulence model selection, and hemolysis post-processing scripts were confirmed correct."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
