      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "The selected turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive model must be justified relative to the flow physics of the COU.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model is selected based on its established performance for rotating machinery flows with adverse pressure gradients. The Giersiepen power-law hemolysis model is used consistently with published FDA pump simulation studies."
    },
